data.description: Great Rosewood Heights location that qualifies for 100% USDA Rural Development Financing.  Schedule your private showing to view this full brick ranch on a large, level lot with fenced back yard.  This classic home offers two masonry fireplaces, oversized two car attached garage, Three Bedrooms, 1 1/2 bath.   Many updates include a waterproofed basement, furnace & Central Air (2018), Roof 2016.   LVP flooring (2023) runs throughout most of the main level of this home.
